Arthur Appleton, a Chicago investor,told the Securities and Exchange Commission he has acquired39,000 shares of Sage Drilling Co Inc, or 5.1 pct of the totaloutstanding common stock.    Appleton said he bought the stock for 116,554 dlrs forinvestment purposes.    Depending on several circumstances, Appleton said he maybuy more Sage common shares, or sell some or all of his currentstake. Reuter&#3;